dry off
Homonym Number:
Word Class:verb
Sense Number:
Definition:[used elsewhere but first recorded in New Zealand] to cease the milking of dairy cows to prepare for calving.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
See:
